WEBVTT

00:00.960 --> 00:02.920
Autumn of the 26th year of Longwu

00:03.440 --> 00:06.040
You ordered the eldest son Sikong Sheng to oversee the state

00:06.320 --> 00:08.560
Then personally led 60,000 troops

00:08.960 --> 00:11.400
With Grand General Zhu Yuanzhi as commander

00:12.040 --> 00:13.640
Zu Yue as left general

00:14.160 --> 00:16.120
Sikong Xu as right general

00:16.440 --> 00:19.040
Marched north to face Shilang

00:28.280 --> 00:31.400
To war

00:32.800 --> 00:35.080
Long live Your Majesty

00:36.680 --> 00:39.080
Long live Your Majesty

