Around Beiyu Pass

00:42.400 --> 00:44.920
Xuan and Wei engaged in a life-and-death struggle

00:45.440 --> 00:47.160
The battle line stretched for thousands of miles

00:47.400 --> 00:48.800
From Qing Province to the Eastern Sea

00:49.160 --> 00:50.320
North to Yiyang City

00:50.440 --> 00:51.800
West to the Luo River

